-- Eni Upgrades Gas Production Estimates at Perla 3 Field Offshore Venezuela
-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 2010-11-15T10:58:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/eni-upgrades-gas-production-estimates-at-perla-3-field-offshore-venezuela.html
Eni SpA said the Perla 3 well
offshore Venezuela is able to produce the equivalent of 2.5
billion barrels of oil, it said in an e-mailed statement today.  “During the production test, the well flowed 68 million
scf per day of gas and 1,350 barrels of condensate per day,”
the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  